speakerBiography.text:
Timothy DeLaGhetto, also known as Traphik, is an Asian American YouTube sensation, rapper, comedian, writer, and videographer. His main YouTube channel has over 2.9 subscribers and 601 million video views as of August 2015.

It features original skits, parodies, rants, and a series called Dear DeLaGhetto. His most popular video has over 79 million views. With 430+ vlogs to date on his second channel, where he documents the adventures of his day to day life, he has garnered 915,000+ subscribers and over 133 million video views.

Timothy is currently one of the cast members on Guy Code and Nick Cannon’s show Wild ‘N Out on MTV2.
